{"tid":1780481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"淺黃老母一直唔信有人比popo打死   直到…","createTime":"2019-12-12T11:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T11:28:13.000Z","uid":31020,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a636331c4ea96b6bccefab7f03148a564b564fd","tid":1780481,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"直到佢朋友問佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">之前個個星期都咁多浮屍，<br />\n但點解區選後呢兩個星期咁靜，而且又一條浮屍都冇？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n家母話佢自己都駁唔到<br />\n深藍老豆聽到起初好唔明<br />\n家母就解釋話，因為冇衝突所以冇人比班popo襯亂打死囉<br />\n<br />\n然後我媽開始唱 tell me what SEVEN you say&hellip;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(佢不嬲唔講粗口，但就不停唱，仲要加句seven<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n佢前排先學完popo，而家仲學埋condom，話想睇condom幾時比人dum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢本身冇facebook，又冇連登igtg個啲。問佢邊到學翻黎，佢話係佢手足喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下邊位手足教到我媽咁醒，可唔可以出黎認咗佢？"},{"pid":"276d93d23fe678a1f8039fa88867c7563b2c247a","tid":1780481,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2567b1dd64a9b956163a6cc6b5fbf5aee1302f","tid":1780481,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"tell me what seven you say<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}